frameDefinitions: A Subset is profiled against the Group it belongs to.
This frame covers words that name Locations as defined politically, or administratively.
The Military of a Possessor (either a nation, institution, or private individual) conducts large-scale activities in a Area to accomplish military or combined military/non-military goals.
This frame contains  words for individuals, i.e. humans, with respect to their Origin.
An Entity began its existence in the context of a Origin, which can be a place,  culture, time period, text, etc.
A System is perceived as complex depending on the intricacy of the interconnectivty of its parts or components.
frameExamples: <t>Of</t> all scenes that evoke rural England, this is one of the loveliest.
These groups are known to have carried out attacks on international coalition forces <t>operating</t> in Afghanistan.
The Christian <t>origin</t> of this quote is from Isaiah 22.
San Diego freeways are a <t>complex</t> array of poorly maintained roads.
listRoleDefinitions: The <fen>Group</fen> of entities which includes the <fen>Subset</fen>.
A stable bounded area.  It is typically the designation of the nouns of Locale-derived frames.
The <fen>Force</fen> carries out the operation. Depending on the size of the operation, this may be as few as one individual or as large as the armed forces of a nation.
The <fen>Area</fen> in which the <fen>Military</fen> is conducting operations.
The nation, group, or situation which the operation opposes.
The <fen>Time</fen> at which the operations are carried out.

The <fen>Origin</fen> is the place where the <fen>Person</fen> was born or lived a salient part of her or his life.  In this frame, it is generally incorporated in the lexical item, but may be separately specified as in the following:
The <fen>Person</fen> is the human being whose <fen>Origin</fen> is specified.
The item whose <fen>Origin</fen> is under discussion.
The place or culture where the <fen>Entity</fen> was produced.
The complete entity or system whose complexity is under consideration.
listRoleExamples: There used to be a forest in that <fex><t>city</t></fex>
<fex>He</fex> died while carrying out counter-IED operations.
Operations <fex>against Afghanistan</fex> continue to be carried out.
He was captured in a covert <fex>arrest</fex> operation carried out by an elite group of highly-trained Marines.
This sort of operation should only be conducted <fex>in open areas</fex>.
Foreigners <fex>from Japan</fex> get short shrift around here.
